subtitle: balance is the means by which one brings
their inner and outer realities into
harmony with each other too much focus
on one or the other brings the opposite
side to its knees and therein we find
ourselves in a state of suffering for
instance there are some who Focus so
much on their internal Journey that they
ignore the needs and demands of the
physical material world and likewise
there are those who focus on their outer
reality and the happenings of the
material and the needs of the flesh so
much that they do not address what is
actually going on within them and cause
more suffering and sorrow in the long
run by ignoring the needs of the Soul
bring balance to your Reality by making
time for both that which is within and
without and much love and blessings on
your
journey
